response.overview: Fucked up is an animated music video created for the band, Bikini Trill, by the artist, Shokka. The video follows two main characters, “LJ” and “Blessed”, as they navigate love and loss in a time when human connection is fleeting. The video is centered around the apartment building in which Bikini Trill recorded their EP; it is set during the pandemic and explores the small windows into peoples’ lives as they cope, carry on, and explore.
response.title: Fucked Up
